# Project Memory for Antigravity

> Purpose: This file is a project memory / brief for an AI coding agent such as Antigravity.
> Use it to understand the current project direction before making changes.

---

## 1. Project Identity

This is an existing Arabic RTL gallery website for customized educational products.

The public website showcases:

- Customized notebooks
- Educational books
- Preschool activity books
- Custom covers
- Planners / daily notebooks
- Children learning materials

The project must NOT be rewritten from scratch.

The current public UI and UX are important and should be preserved.

---

## 2. Main User Goal

The final goal is to create a simple production-ready system where a non-technical admin user can manage the gallery easily from a phone.

The main admin user should be able to:

1. Login to an admin dashboard.
2. Add product categories/types.
3. Upload images from phone gallery/storage.
4. Choose which category each image belongs to.
5. Mark images as featured.
6. Edit images/items.
7. Delete images/items.
8. Manage WhatsApp/contact settings.
9. See changes reflected on the public gallery.

The admin dashboard must be extremely simple and mobile-first.

---

