## 5. Admin Dashboard Vision

The admin dashboard should be:

- Arabic only
- RTL
- Mobile-first
- Designed mainly for smartphone use
- Simple enough for a non-technical person
- Based on cards and large touch-friendly buttons
- Avoiding complex tables
- Easy to use with one hand when possible

Expected admin sections:

### Login

Fields:

- Email
- Password
- Login button

### First-Time Setup

If there are no categories yet, show a setup panel:

- Title: `لنبدأ بإضافة أنواع المنتجات`
- Description: `أضيفي أنواع الدفاتر والكراريس التي تريدين عرضها في المعرض.`
- Input: `اسم النوع`
- Button: `إضافة النوع`
- Show added types as chips/cards
- Button: `حفظ الأنواع والانتقال إلى المعرض`

After saving categories, the setup section should disappear/collapse and the gallery management area should appear.

### Main Admin Page

Sections:

1. Add image
2. Current gallery
3. Manage categories
4. Site settings

### Add Image Flow

The flow must be very short:

1. Choose image from phone/gallery
2. Preview image
3. Choose category/type
4. Optionally enter title
5. Toggle featured
6. Save

The user must never manually type image URLs.

### Current Gallery

Each gallery item should appear as a card:

- Image
- Title
- Category
- Featured badge if featured
- Edit button
- Delete button

### Edit Image

A mobile-friendly modal or bottom sheet:

- Current image preview
- Replace image button
- Title input
- Category select
- Featured toggle
- Save changes
- Cancel

### Delete Image

Show confirmation:

`هل أنتِ متأكدة من حذف هذه الصورة؟`

Buttons:

- `حذف`
- `إلغاء`

### Manage Categories

Collapsed by default under:

`إدارة الأنواع`

Features:

- Add category
- Edit category
- Delete category

If a category has images, deletion should be blocked or require safe handling.

Recommended message:

`لا يمكن حذف هذا النوع لأنه يحتوي على صور. احذفي الصور أو انقليها أولًا.`

### Site Settings

Collapsed by default under:

`إعدادات الموقع`

Fields:

- WhatsApp number
- Default WhatsApp message
- Hero title
- Hero subtitle
- Meta title
- Meta description

