## 17. Image Upload Explanation

The admin selects images from phone storage/gallery.

However, the image cannot remain only on the phone, because visitors cannot access the admin's phone files.

Therefore, the upload flow must be:

```txt
Phone file picker
↓
Frontend receives File object
↓
Frontend sends File to backend as multipart/form-data
↓
Backend uploads file to Cloudinary
↓
Cloudinary returns public URL
↓
Backend stores URL in PostgreSQL
↓
Frontend/public gallery displays image URL
```

This is the correct meaning of “upload from phone storage.”

